title: Bikewatchers
description: Bikewatching is an interactive web-based data visualization tool that explores bike traffic patterns in the Boston and Cambridge area. Using real-time station data, historical ride data, and geographic mapping, this project provides insights into bike-sharing activity, station usage, and traffic flow.
